          "cookies": [],
          "content": {
            "size": 9070,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"data\":{\"maintenanceRequestComments\":{\"edges\":[{\"cursor\":\"MQ\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"7ff4fabd-dcfa-4896-b834-50e6b9436341\",\"body\":\"This task can be closed. Everything is fixed.\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":true,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-28T13:24:14.162Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"3cb297be-8425-42fe-afbf-80b1eb6fc324\",\"fullName\":\"Earl Co (ECO Systems)\",\"isAdmin\":false,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"2316ec5b-2935-428b-9416-620b5851f675\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/2316ec5b-2935-428b-9416-620b5851f675/profile_image/45d39fd5-7ca3-4bcb-bd6b-66e9fcce20bf/Earl_Co_Profile.jpg\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"Mg\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"ca5e189d-6e67-462c-b090-adfcfb697da2\",\"body\":\"Hello Julia,\\n\\nHas JobConnect contacted you to schedule yet? If not, please feel free to reach out to them at (703) 728-4321 to schedule at your earliest convenience and let us know the date and time once confirmed so we can stay on top of this for you.\\n\\nThanks\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-27T12:01:02.076Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"1478cfe5-f605-48e8-8456-1b5efbd8710a\",\"fullName\":\"Maintenance Coordinator\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"5bc44574-a74b-42ee-8a9b-d47a4b6fa677\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/3a4cc05c-d138-437c-b392-5c23abf033b9/profile_image/091e1341-0c74-4584-a90e-48277a5fb41f/TAW_180611_NEWS_TravelAgentsAreHappy.jpg\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"Mw\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"3a82dfb7-ff38-4f52-b80c-b98009439432\",\"body\":\"Hi Julia,\\n\\nThat is amazing to hear!\\n\\nThanks so much for confirming that this issue has been resolved for you.  We'll go ahead and close this out once the billing tasks have been completed. Please let us know if we may be of further assistance.\\n\\nHave a great day,\\n\\nBest,\\nNancy\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-26T00:28:38.335Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"9c891693-bbe5-4820-8fc8-507c1eb47221\",\"fullName\":\"Nancy Kay\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"e34218bc-b534-4ac8-8faf-8c2447de77c0\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/e34218bc-b534-4ac8-8faf-8c2447de77c0/profile_image/a87c268e-724a-4d83-817a-3647e375edb8/20250105_172731 (1).jpg\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"NA\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"f853c0ff-a58f-4e48-9723-7c8693a77004\",\"body\":\"Everything is fixed thank you\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-25T23:40:07.541Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"d3954764-9ea7-4072-b4ef-b87f935f0a80\",\"fullName\":\"Julia Price\",\"isAdmin\":false,\"vendorProfile\":null,\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"NQ\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"12f0b285-f43a-45f7-8d74-177ed799df81\",\"body\":\"Hi Julia,\\nThank you for the update.\\n\\nPlease let us know if they reach out to you. If not, we can contact them directly to help schedule the appointment. We have your availability on file, so we can coordinate accordingly and get this sorted out.\\n\\nPlease let us know if there is anything further we can assist with.\\n\\nThank you,\\nManuel S\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-25T00:46:39.466Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"e60e0958-3421-4a1c-ba36-cdb4bd29f38b\",\"fullName\":\"Manuel Siles\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"d6d858fe-9cd4-4db4-93af-2ffc60056fed\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profile_image/cddeca5d-d7f4-46ca-b63b-5011b9db1502/69096.png\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"Ng\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"32d0fd28-9da8-4016-808b-4f826c6a7c7d\",\"body\":\"Okay thank you. Waiting for them to contact me.\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T21:19:16.051Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"d3954764-9ea7-4072-b4ef-b87f935f0a80\",\"fullName\":\"Julia Price\",\"isAdmin\":false,\"vendorProfile\":null,\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"Nw\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"2423c5c9-1592-4426-abd7-02f08c424cc4\",\"body\":\"Hello Julia,\\n\\nThis has been assigned to JobConnect (703) 728-4321. They will be reaching out to schedule with you directly. Please let us know the date and time scheduled once confirmed so we may stay on top of this for you.\\n\\nThanks,\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T19:57:13.075Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"1478cfe5-f605-48e8-8456-1b5efbd8710a\",\"fullName\":\"Maintenance Coordinator\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"5bc44574-a74b-42ee-8a9b-d47a4b6fa677\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/3a4cc05c-d138-437c-b392-5c23abf033b9/profile_image/091e1341-0c74-4584-a90e-48277a5fb41f/TAW_180611_NEWS_TravelAgentsAreHappy.jpg\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"OA\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"ee5b66fd-9b32-429d-a896-c6ed126344d8\",\"body\":\"Hi Julia,\\n\\nThanks for the update. We'll proceed with getting somebody out for you and we'll let you know as soon as we have an update. Please let us know if you have any questions or concerns.\\n\\nThanks,\\nNancy\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T17:27:04.436Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"9c891693-bbe5-4820-8fc8-507c1eb47221\",\"fullName\":\"Nancy Kay\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"e34218bc-b534-4ac8-8faf-8c2447de77c0\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/e34218bc-b534-4ac8-8faf-8c2447de77c0/profile_image/a87c268e-724a-4d83-817a-3647e375edb8/20250105_172731 (1).jpg\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"OQ\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"860fdd06-784c-4472-8f2c-145d819cfd6e\",\"body\":\"It is a slow leak under the sink in bathroom. The bathtub drain is very slow now.\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T15:02:29.413Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"d3954764-9ea7-4072-b4ef-b87f935f0a80\",\"fullName\":\"Julia Price\",\"isAdmin\":false,\"vendorProfile\":null,\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"MTA\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"a877d35e-58b8-4a15-8037-fd2fe947d5c7\",\"body\":\"Okay thank you!\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T15:01:42.607Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"d3954764-9ea7-4072-b4ef-b87f935f0a80\",\"fullName\":\"Julia Price\",\"isAdmin\":false,\"vendorProfile\":null,\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"},{\"cursor\":\"MTE\",\"node\":{\"id\":\"d35f4e20-19ff-4b74-84ff-9fe4cacd3cb9\",\"body\":\"Hello Julia,\\n\\nThank you for bringing both of these issues to our attention.\\n\\nFor the bathtub drain, we understand you mentioned you are unable to plunge or snake it. As a simple alternative, you can try a baking soda and vinegar flush. Start by pouring boiling water down the drain to help loosen any buildup, then add one cup of baking soda followed by one cup of vinegar. Let the mixture sit for about 15 minutes, then rinse with more boiling water. Please let us know if this does not help, and we will arrange for a technician to assist.\\n\\nRegarding the leaking sink, could you please confirm where the sink is located and whether the leak is constant or only occurs when the water is running? From the photo, it appears the leak may be coming from the bottom of the sink, but please confirm if that is correct. If the leak is active, we recommend shutting off the water supply using the valves located underneath the sink. If you are unable to locate them, please let us know. If the leak is not active, placing a bucket underneath and avoiding use of the sink would be helpful while we arrange next steps.\\n\\nAdditionally, if the leak is active, please let us know the extent of it, whether it is a slow drip or a heavier flow with pressure. A short video of the leak would also be very helpful for us to better assess the situation.\\n\\nRegards,\\n\\nTed.\",\"isHiddenFromTenants\":false,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-24T11:12:13.105Z\",\"createdBy\":{\"id\":\"2a50f619-e0bd-480d-9209-0cb1acf39b1c\",\"fullName\":\"Ted Odera\",\"isAdmin\":true,\"vendorProfile\":{\"id\":\"4cc13257-14f7-47e9-a918-737ac64203ed\",\"profileImageUrl\":\"//hemlane-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/vendor_profiles/4cc13257-14f7-47e9-a918-737ac64203ed/profile_image/ecd8fe02-7625-4a45-b97d-fbf503a6aec6/1690385721295.jfif\",\"__typename\":\"VendorProfile\"},\"__typename\":\"User\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestComment\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentEdge\"}],\"pageInfo\":{\"startCursor\":\"MQ\",\"endCursor\":\"MTE\",\"hasPreviousPage\":false,\"hasNextPage\":false,\"__typename\":\"PageInfo\"},\"__typename\":\"MaintenanceRequestCommentConnection\"}}}"
